		<h2 class='diff-currentversion-title'>Revision as of 17:03, 9 September 2014</h2>
<div class="hatnote">This article is about the Tolstoy novel.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/War_and_Peace_(disambiguation)" title="War and Peace (disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig">War and Peace (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox vcard" style="width:22em">
<caption style="font-style:italic;padding-bottom:0.2em;">War and Peace</caption>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="/wiki/File:Tolstoy_-_War_and_Peace_-_first_edition,_1869.jpg" class="image" title="Front page of War and Peace, first edition, 1869 (Russian)"><img alt="Front page of War and Peace, first edition, 1869 (Russian)" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/af/Tolstoy_-_War_and_Peace_-_first_edition%2C_1869.jpg" width="235" height="341" data-file-width="235" data-file-height="341" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left">Author</th>
<td><a href="/wiki/Leo_Tolstoy" title="Leo Tolstoy">Leo Tolstoy</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left">Original&#160;title</th>
<td><span lang="" xml:lang=""><i>Война и миръ</i></span></td>
