<li><i>War and Peace</i> is featured in the <i><a href="/wiki/Seinfeld" title="Seinfeld">Seinfeld</a></i> episode "<i><a href="/wiki/The_Marine_Biologist" title="The Marine Biologist">The Marine Biologist</a></i>", when Jerry jokes that the novel's original title was "War, What Is It Good For?" Elaine disastrously repeats the joke to a famous Russian writer.</li>
