<li id="cite_note-49"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-49">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20080618053118/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/discography/index.jsp?pid=2114&amp;aid=1147828">War and Peace</a> at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a> (archived June 18, 2008)<sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Link_rot" title="Wikipedia:Link rot"><span title="&#160;since April 2014">dead link</span></a></i>]</span></sup>. Billboard.com. June 17, 2008</span></li>
